channel.title: How to get free DOMAIN names for a year [USA only]
channel.description:
well i was looking around when i found this site
[url=http://www.domainlagoon.com]http://www.domainlagoon.com[/url]
basicly you get a free domain when u register and anwser a few questions (i think) and after that year and u have earned enought points (dunno how u get them) you get the domain for free another year. other wise u have to pay $9.99
IMPORTANT!
i have not tryed this because i don't live in the USA but anyone who does try it please tell me what information it asks for so i can post it here.
